    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Time to familiarize yourself with the <code>ArrayList</code> API and more:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html?is-external=true\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>ArrayList</code> at Java 6 API Documentation</a>  </p>\n\n<p>For your immediate question:</p>\n\n<p><code>mainList.get(3);</code></p>\n"
