    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<pre><code>mainList.get(3);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For future reference, you should refer to the Java API for these types of questions:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/1.4.2/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://download.oracle.com/javase/1.4.2/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html</a></p>\n\n<p>It's a useful thing!</p>\n"
