    "body" : "<p>Try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayListname.get(index);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Where <code>index</code> is the position in the index and <code>ArrayListname</code> is the name of the Arraylist as in your case is mainList.</p>\n"
